376
00:16:30,801 --> 00:16:31,961
Min Quanquan.

377
00:16:31,961 --> 00:16:33,201
You're eating it without me!

378
00:16:33,321 --> 00:16:34,961
Have you been naughty recently?

379
00:16:35,162 --> 00:16:36,321
No, I've been good.

380
00:16:36,321 --> 00:16:37,762
