♪I don't wanna break a promise♪

389
00:16:57,340 --> 00:16:59,620
♪Braving us♪

390
00:16:59,900 --> 00:17:02,660
♪I just wanna stay here till you♪

391
00:17:02,740 --> 00:17:04,940
♪Feel my love♪

392
00:17:05,380 --> 00:17:09,260
